{"id":317197,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/【图说天朝】同学情深也不能同床共寝/","date":"2013-10-09T07:56:15Z","modified":"2013-10-09T07:56:15Z","title":"【图说天朝】同学情深也不能同床共寝","content":"<p>@人人网：日前，浙江慈溪市观城中学高一（7）班两对男小伙伴因同床共寝，受到全校通报批评处分！学校指出，学校床小，难以承受过多重量；同学情深，也不体现在同床共枕。望广大同学以此为鉴，严格遵守就寝纪律，切实提高安全意识……</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/0a0a41a8502df32b1faf740d7ba46d01.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-317198\" alt=\"0a0a41a8502df32b1faf740d7ba46d01\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/0a0a41a8502df32b1faf740d7ba46d01.jpg\" width=\"460\" height=\"692\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/0a0a41a8502df32b1faf740d7ba46d01.jpg 460w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/10/0a0a41a8502df32b1faf740d7ba46d01-199x300.jpg 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,20534],"tags":[9364,23930]}